title: Kevin McCarthy faces possible floor fight in speaker bid as conservatives back Daniel Webster
text: The conservative House Freedom Caucus announced Wednesday that it would back Rep. Daniel Webster to be the next speaker, which would provide enough support to the Republican conference to deny the position to establishment favorite Kevin McCarthy, the current majority leader.
